    <div class="content">
      <h1>Benefits of Electric Vehicles</h1>
      <p>Electric vehicles have many benefits that make them superior to conventional vehicles. Here are some of the main benefits of electric vehicles:</p>
      <div class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit">
          <img src="environment.png" alt="Environment icon">
          <h2>Environmentally Friendly</h2>
          <p>Electric vehicles produce zero tailpipe emissions, which means they do not contribute to air pollution and climate change. They also use renewable energy sources, such as solar and wind power, which reduce the dependence on fossil fuels and their harmful impacts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <img src="money.png" alt="Money icon">
          <h2>Economically Efficient</h2>
          <p>Electric vehicles have lower operating and maintenance costs than conventional vehicles. They save money on fuel, as electricity is cheaper than gasoline or diesel. They also have fewer moving parts and require less frequent servicing and repairs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <img src="car.png" alt="Car icon">
          <h2>Technologically Advanced</h2>
          <p>Electric vehicles have many features that make them more convenient and comfortable to drive. They have instant torque, which means they accelerate faster and smoother than conventional vehicles. They also have regenerative braking, which recovers energy from braking and reduces wear and tear. They also have smart features, such as navigation, entertainment, and safety systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
